A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Safety – 9–1–1 Trust Fund – 9–8–8 Suicide Prevention Hotline
3 FOR the purpose of authorizing the use of the 9–1–1 Trust Fund for certain expenditures
4 that support the 9–8–8 suicide prevention hotline; altering a certain restriction on
5 the use of the 9–1–1 Trust Fund to prohibit funds from being used for expenses solely
6 related to the 9–8–8 suicide prevention hotline, instead of preventing the use of funds
7 for any costs associated with the 9–8–8 suicide prevention hotline; and generally
8 relating to the 9–1–1 Trust Fund and the 9–8–8 suicide prevention hotline.
